des: Here at Oxford school of motoring we cater for all stages of learning to drive. From complete beginners to advanced motorway lessons. We have been established for over 40 years and have passed thousands of pupils, so we are very experienced. Nervous well dont be we offer a warm and friendly service give us a call on 01865 770771 or mobile 07721315249. Or go to chrissmith.website to arrange a lesson.
